---
title: Loaded Fajita Potato Wedges with Fried Egg, Pepper Jack & Zesty Garlic Mayo
description: You’ve had fajitas, and you’ve had potato wedges, but you’ve probably never had either of those things quite like this. Potatoes roast with green bell pepper, onion, and our signature Fajita Spice; meanwhile, you whip up some surprising sides (garlic mayo and fried eggs—heyo!). Wedges are topped with cheddar and pepper jack, then returned to the oven until melty and “nacho-esque.” Everything’s garnished with diced tomato, eggs, and mayo drizzle, then eaten straight from the pan for a meal that's the best of two tasty worlds.
